    "Bottom: Two simulated populations of lensed quasars are shown, one from Oguri and Marshall (2010) and an identical one generated with lens potential ellipticity and external shear distributions with lower and higher mean values respectively (0.15 and 0.1 as opposed to 0.3 and 0.05, based on Luhtaru et al. 2021).",
    "The footprint of the GERLUMPH database is also shown",
